---
title: Butternut and Brussels Sprout Risotto with Sweet Honey Pepitas
description: When you’re seeking comfort, nothing beats a soul-warming dish like risotto. We've filled this one out with hearty seasonal vegetables like Brussels sprouts and butternut squash, then added pancetta and honey-coated pepitas for a sweet and salty accent. Loaded with vibrant colors and flavors, it’s as delightful to look at as it is to taste.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/butternut-squash-risotto-with-pa-ab06544a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/butternut-squash-risotto-with-pa-d855328d.pdf
